  "meta": {
    "source": "toy",
    "description": "Rounded-block-clip prototype fixture. 4 horizontal + 4 vertical residential streets form a 3\u00d73 grid of 9 fully-bounded blocks. Irregularities: VW3 bends NE from (40,60) to (60,160) (top-right blocks become trapezoidal + bent-chain regression); HW3 jogs up from z=40 to z=60 between x=0 and x=20 (saw-tooth top edge on middle blocks); a dead-end stub branches N off HW3 at (25,60), tip at (25,90). Re-run cartograph/derive-toy.js after editing."
  },
